class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Contract\\Extension\\CommandHandlerInterface"
type: interface
summary: "Defines the contract for command handlers within the AgentCore extension system, enabling type-safe dispatch and transformation of command payloads. It ensures that handlers can validate command kinds and safely map execution contexts to structured results."
